OL,7,FFormer Page Three model Samantha Fox
OL,8,Fthreatened to knock a police officer's
OL,9,Fteeth out as he attempted to remove
OL,10,Fher from a plane after a drunken
OL,11,Fincident on a British Airways flight,
OL,12,Fa court has heard.
